file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

components:
  schemas:
    Artist:
      type: object
      properties:
        leftHand:
          nullable: true
          allOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/AnyThing"
        rightHand:
          nullable: true
          allOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Color"

    AnyThing:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Color"
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Food"

    Color:
      type: string
      enum:
        - red
        - green
        - blue

    Food:
      type: string
      enum:
        - apple
        - banana
        - pizza
